The paper deals with improving image classification using deep learning models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) research. The proposed method involves using reinforcement learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the problem of overfitting, which is a common issue in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper focuses on medical image analysis, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM) research.
